{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I’d like to dedicate this one to all the women in South Africa --"},{"time":6000,"text":"those women who refused to dwindle in the midst of apartheid."},{"time":11000,"text":"And, of course, I’m dedicating it also to my grandmother,"},{"time":17000,"text":"whom I think really played quite a lot of important roles,"},{"time":20000,"text":"especially for me when I was an activist, and being harassed by the police."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26000,"text":"You will recall that in 1976, June 16, the students of South Africa boycotted"},{"time":31000,"text":"the language of Afrikaans as the medium of the oppressor,"},{"time":35000,"text":"as they were sort of like really told"},{"time":38000,"text":"that they must do everything in Afrikaans --"},{"time":41000,"text":"biology, mathematics -- and what about our languages?"},{"time":45000,"text":"And the students wanted to speak to the government,"},{"time":49000,"text":"and police answered with bullets."},{"time":51000,"text":"So every year, June 16, we will commemorate"},{"time":53000,"text":"all those comrades or students who died."},{"time":57000,"text":"And I was very young then. I think I was 11 years,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and I started asking questions,"},{"time":65000,"text":"and that’s when my political education started."},{"time":68000,"text":"And I joined, later on, the youth organization"},{"time":71000,"text":"under the African National Congress."},{"time":74000,"text":"So as part of organizing this and whatever,"},{"time":77000,"text":"this commemoration, the police will round us up"},{"time":80000,"text":"as they call us leaders."},{"time":83000,"text":"And I used to run away from home,"},{"time":85000,"text":"when I know that maybe the police might be coming"},{"time":88000,"text":"around the ninth or 10th of June or so."},{"time":91000,"text":"And my grandmother one time said,"},{"time":93000,"text":"\"No, look, you’re not going to run away."},{"time":96000,"text":"This is your place, you stay here.\""},{"time":100000,"text":"And indeed, the police came -- because they’ll just arrest us"},{"time":104000,"text":"and put us in jail and release us whenever they feel like, after the 20th or so."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109000,"text":"So it was on the 10th of June, and they came, and they surrounded the house,"},{"time":114000,"text":"and my grandmother switched off all the lights in the house,"},{"time":120000,"text":"and opened the kitchen door."},{"time":123000,"text":"And she said to them, \"Vusi's here, and you're not going to take him tonight."},{"time":128000,"text":"I'm tired of you having to come here, harassing us,"},{"time":131000,"text":"while your children are sleeping peacefully in your homes."},{"time":133000,"text":"He is here, and you're not going to take him."},{"time":136000,"text":"I've got a bowl full of boiling water -- the first one who comes in here, gets it.\""},{"time":143000,"text":"And they left."},{"time":146000,"text":"(Applause) (Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":179000,"text":"♫ Thula Mama, Thula Mama, Thula Mama, Thula Mama. ♫"},{"time":184000,"text":"♫ Through the mist of the tears in your eyes on my childhood memory, ♫"},{"time":192000,"text":"♫ I know the truth in your smile, ♫"},{"time":196000,"text":"♫ I know the truth in your smile, ♫"},{"time":199000,"text":"♫ piercing through the gloom of my ignorance. ♫"},{"time":202000,"text":"♫ Oh, there is a mama lying down sleeping ♫"},{"time":207000,"text":"♫ you're very ill and your heart crying. ♫"},{"time":211000,"text":"♫ Wondering, wondering, wondering, wondering where is this world coming to. ♫"},{"time":219000,"text":"♫ Is it right the children have to fend for themselves? No, no, no, no, no. no. ♫"},{"time":224000,"text":"♫ Is it right heaping trouble on an old lady's head? ♫"},{"time":228000,"text":"♫ So unlucky faceless people. ♫"},{"time":234000,"text":"♫ Thula Mama Mama, Thula Mama. Thula Mama Mama. ♫"},{"time":266000,"text":"♫ Thula Mama, Thula Mama, Thula Mama Mama, Thula Mama ♫"},{"time":271000,"text":"♫ Tomorrow it’s going to be better. ♫"},{"time":276000,"text":"♫ Tomorrow it's going to be better to climb, Mama. ♫"},{"time":281000,"text":"♫ Thula Mama, Thula Mama. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":321000,"text":"♫ Am I to break into the song like the blues man or troubadour. ♫"},{"time":328000,"text":"♫ And then from long distance in no blues club am I to sing, ♫"},{"time":334000,"text":"♫ baby, baby, baby, baby, baby, baby, baby, baby, baby, baby, baby, baby. ♫"},{"time":344000,"text":"♫ Should I now stop singing of love, ♫"},{"time":350000,"text":"♫ now that my memory’s surrounded by blood? ♫"},{"time":353000,"text":"♫ Sister, why oh why do we at times mistake a pimple for a cancer? ♫"},{"time":372000,"text":"♫ So who are they who says, no more love poems now? ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":377000,"text":"♫ I want to sing a song of love ♫"},{"time":380000,"text":"♫ for that woman who jumped the fences pregnant ♫"},{"time":383000,"text":"♫ and still gave birth to a healthy child. ♫"},{"time":395000,"text":"♫ Softly I walk into the sun rays of the smile ♫"},{"time":402000,"text":"♫ that will ignite my love song, my song of life, ♫"},{"time":410000,"text":"♫ my song of love, my song of life, my song of love, ♫"},{"time":420000,"text":"♫ my song of life, my song of love, my song of life. ♫"},{"time":432000,"text":"♫ Ooh, I’ve not tried to run away from song, ♫"},{"time":436000,"text":"♫ I hear a persistent voice, more powerful than the enemy bombs. ♫"},{"time":442000,"text":"♫ The song that washed our lives and the rains of our blood. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":472000,"text":"♫ My song of love and my song of life, my song of love, ♫"},{"time":479000,"text":"♫ my song of life, my song of love, ♫"},{"time":486000,"text":"♫ my song of life, my song of love -- I want everybody to sing with me -- ♫"},{"time":491000,"text":"♫ my song of life, my song of love, my song of life -- everybody sing with me -- ♫"},{"time":499000,"text":"♫ my song of life, my song of love -- I can’t hear you -- ♫"},{"time":504000,"text":"♫ my song of love, my song of life -- you can do better -- ♫"},{"time":509000,"text":"♫ my song of life, my song of love -- keep singing, keep singing -- ♫"},{"time":515000,"text":"♫ my song of love, my song of life, yes, my song of love -- ♫"},{"time":522000,"text":"♫ you can do better than that -- ♫"},{"time":524000,"text":"♫ my song of life, yes, my song of love, my song of life, my song of love -- ♫"},{"time":533000,"text":"♫ keep singing, keep singing, keep singing -- my song of love. ♫"},{"time":536000,"text":"♫ Oh yeah. My song of -- a love song, my song of life. Sing. A love song, my song of life. Sing. ♫"},{"time":550000,"text":"♫ Love song, my song of life. Sing. Love song, my song of life. Sing. ♫"},{"time":561000,"text":"♫ Love song, my song of life. Sing. Love song, my song of life. ♫"},{"time":571000,"text":"♫ Love song, my song of life. ♫"},{"time":577000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}